<p begin="00:00:08.660" end="00:00:10.800" style="s2"> I am not a materialist (philosophical doctrine) anymore.</p>
<p begin="00:00:11.100" end="00:00:13.680" style="s2"> I don&#39;t think the world is made of matter.</p>
