<p begin="00:05:10.080" end="00:05:13.220" style="s2"> John Milton wrote Paradise Lost for two reasons:</p>
<p begin="00:05:13.360" end="00:05:15.540" style="s2"> The first is to justify God&#39;s ways to people.</p>
<p begin="00:05:15.740" end="00:05:27.640" style="s2"> The second reason for his writings is the arrangement of mythology stories that were marginal to ecclesiastical Christianity</p>
